<main>
	<header class="page-header" style="background: url('/images/lifestyle/texting.jpg') no-repeat center;">
		<div class="header-block-container">
			<div class="text-block">
				<h1>Heal your gut without leaving home.</h1>
				<p>Digestive diseases and disorders are not only uncomfortable but left untreated, can lead to more serious, chronic illness. </p>
				<a href="/contact.html" class="button-light">Request more info today</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</header>

	<section class="image-text-block-container" id="about">
		<%= image_tag 'lifestyle/group.jpg', alt: '' %>
		<div class="text-block">
			<h2>Second Brain Healthcare is a digital healthcare company dedicated to improving outcomes and lowering the cost to diagnose and treat functional gut diseases.</h2>
			<p>Our technology-enabled platform provides patients with a fast and accurate diagnosis and unparalleled access to an integrated, multi-disciplinary, and collaborative team of gut health specialists throughout their patient journey.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="fact-block-container" id="facts">
		<header class="section-header centered">
			<h2>Functional Gut Disease and Disorders are at an <strong>All-Time High and their impact on patient Quality of life is significant</strong></h2>
			<p>Our technology-enabled platform provides patients with a fast and accurate diagnosis and unparalleled access to an integrated, multi-disciplinary, and collaborative team of gut health specialists throughout their patient journey.</p>
		</header>
		<ul class="facts">
			<li>
				<span>70M</span>
				<p>people in the United States are diagnosed each year with some form of digestive disease or disorder, most of which are chronic.</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<span>74%</span>
				<p>of those people have lived with their GI symptoms for more than six months.</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<span>14</span>
				<p>hours per week of lost productivity in patients with digestive diseases.</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<span>25% to 30%</span>
				<p>of digestive disease patients suffer from depression or anxiety, a rate up to 6 times higher than the control population.</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<span>20%</span>
				<p>(at least 73 days) a year of activity is restricted by digestive disease patients.</p>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>
	
	<div class="callout" style="background: url('/images/lifestyle/reading.jpg') no-repeat center;">
		<div class="callout-block-container">
			<h2>Our gut tells us there has to be a better way</h2>
		</div>
	</div>
	
	<section class="wrapper" id="for-you">
		<div class="checkbox-block-container">
			<header class="section-header centered">
				<h2>Is Second Brain for you:</h2>
				<p> We believe that everyone deserves a life without discomfort or pain. Take the following quiz to see if Second Brain is right for you (check all that apply):</p>
			</header>
			<div class="form">
				<script type="text/javascript" src="https://form.jotform.com/jsform/92668599525174"></script>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="grid-block-container" id="how-it-works">
		<header class="section-header centered">
			<h2>Integrated gut health care, digitally delivered.</h2>
			<p>How it works:</p>
		</header>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<div class="image-block">
					<%= image_tag 'lifestyle/workout.jpg', alt: '' %>
				</div>
				<h3>Diagnose</h3>
				<p>Our digital diagnostic tool helps patients get an accurate diagnosis within days and without visiting a doctor's office.</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<div class="image-block">
					<%= image_tag 'lifestyle/outside.jpg', alt: '' %>
				</div>
				<h3>Treat</h3>
				<p>Our digital therapeutic offers personalized, AI-powered care plans based on evidence-based treatment protocols designed to minimize the use of prescription drugs, as well as the best-in-class educational resources per diagnosis.</p>
			</li>
			<li>
				<div class="image-block">
					<%= image_tag 'lifestyle/cooking.jpg', alt: '' %>
				</div>
				<h3>Support</h3>
				<p>Our platform brings together an integrated, multidisciplinary team of specialists to effectively manage chronic gut disease and flag and treat flare ups as they occur.</p>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section class="wrapper" id="our-approach">
		<div class="process-block-container">
			<header class="section-header centered">
				<h2>Our Approach</h2>
				<p>Taking care of your gut is not an easy task and our team is here to heal you and then help you sustain a new level of health.</p>
			</header>
			<%= image_tag 'lifestyle/approach.png', alt: '', class: 'graphic' %>
			<a href="/contact.html" class="button-neutral"">Request more info today</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</main>

